chunks.cleaned_english_translation:
<speak>
  On the Octave of the Lord<break time="500ms"/>
    On the eighth day, he was named Jesus after being circumcised, marking the moment a cleansed man became a child of the Lord.
  
</speak>
chunks.original_latin:
In Octava Domini. Accepit et nomen jam circumcisus Iesus,
Ut mundatus homo sit soboles Domini.
